                                                           BUSINESS QUESTIONS
What differentiates high-value customers from low-value customers?

                                      QUERY
SELECT
CASE
WHEN lifetime_value > 1500 then 'high value customers'
ELSE 'low value customers'
END AS Customers_status,
ROUND(AVG(discount_usage_rate),2) avg_discount,
ROUND(AVG(lifetime_value) ,2)total_revenue,
ROUND(AVG(login_frequency),2),
ROUND(AVG(product_reviews_written),2),
ROUND(AVG(cart_abandonment_rate),2)
FROM ecommerce_data
GROUP BY Customers_status;

                                        Insight:
High-value customers not only generate more revenue but also show higher engagement, such as more logins and more interaction with products compared
to low-value customers.

                                     Recommendation: 
We can reward high-value customers with benefits like loyalty rewards, while also encouraging low-value customers to increase their engagement and purchases.

